####################
# 完整流程测试（自动化）
####################

### 🔄 完整流程 - 1. 注册
# @name flowRegister
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "workflow_test",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "流程测试用户",
  "email": "workflow@campuslink.com",
  "phone": "13600136000",
  "schoolId": 1,
  "role": "student"
}


### 🔄 完整流程 - 2. 使用注册返回的 Token 获取用户信息
@flowToken = {{flowRegister.response.body.data.token}}

GET {{baseUrl}}/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{flowToken}}


### 🔄 完整流程 - 3. 刷新 Token
# @name flowRefresh
@flowRefreshToken = {{flowRegister.response.body.data.refreshToken}}

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Refresh-Token: {{flowRefreshToken}}


### 🔄 完整流程 - 4. 使用新 Token 获取用户信息
@flowNewToken = {{flowRefresh.response.body.data.token}}

GET {{baseUrl}}/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{flowNewToken}}


### 🔄 完整流程 - 5. 退出登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{flowNewToken}}


