### 📋 任务-0: 注册测试用户（用于任务模块测试）
# @name taskTestRegister
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ta1sk_test_user",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "任务测试用户",
  "email": "task_tet@campuslink.com",
  "phone": "13733000000",
  "schoolId": 1,
  "role": "student"
}

### 📋 任务-1: 发布任务
# @name publishTask
POST {{baseUrl}}/task/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "帮忙取快递 - 顺丰快递",
  "content": "我在上课不方便去拿快递，希望有人帮我取一下，地点在学校北门顺丰驿站，取货码1234",
  "taskType": "errand",
  "rewardPoints": 5,
  "location": "学校北门顺丰驿站",
  "deadline": "2025-11-09T18:00:00"
}


### 📋 任务-2: 获取任务列表（所有用户可访问）
GET {{baseUrl}}/task/list?page=1&pageSize=10


### 📋 任务-3: 获取任务列表（按类型筛选）
GET {{baseUrl}}/task/list?taskType=errand&page=1&pageSize=10


### 📋 任务-4: 获取任务列表（按状态筛选 - 待接单）
GET {{baseUrl}}/task/list?status=0&page=1&pageSize=10


### 📋 任务-5: 获取任务详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/task/1
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}


### 📋 任务-6: 注册接单者
# @name taskAccepter
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "task_accepter",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "热心接单者",
  "email": "accepter@campuslink.com",
  "phone": "13933000001",
  "schoolId": 1,
  "role": "student"
}


### 📋 任务-7: 接单
POST {{baseUrl}}/task/1/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}


### 📋 任务-8: 完成任务（只有发布者可以标记完成）
POST {{baseUrl}}/task/1/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}


### 📋 任务-9: 获取我发布的任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/task/my/published?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}


### 📋 任务-10: 获取我接受的任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/task/my/accepted?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}


### 📋 任务-11: 发布另一个任务用于取消测试
# @name publishTask2
POST {{baseUrl}}/task/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "代签到 - 英语课",
  "content": "明天上午10点英语课帮忙签个到，教室在A栋201",
  "taskType": "sign",
  "rewardPoints": 3,
  "location": "A栋201教室"
}


### 📋 任务-12: 取消任务（只有发布者可以取消）
POST {{baseUrl}}/task/2/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}
